data.title: Enterprise Resource Planning
data.meta_description: Exel Project - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document lists 12 Oracle SOA resources including their profile details like name, contact number, email, skills, and current company. It shows that 5 resources have skills in Oracle SOA, 1 in Oracle SOA Lead, 3 in Oracle SOA Developer, and 2 in SOA Developer. The resources are currently working for companies like Oracle, Capgemini, Infosys, Accenture, Dell Technologies, and SkyOnn Technologies.
